tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE EarthquakeData (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    latitude FLOAT,
    longitude FLOAT,
    magnitude FLOAT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE EarthquakeCoordinates (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  earthquake_id INT,
  latitude FLOAT,
  longitude FLOAT,
  FOREIGN KEY (earthquake_id) REFERENCES EarthquakeLocations(id)
);
